en a wis caster in the kill group they would have taken it right away?  And what of the shoulder item that rotted, forever WASTED because someone told us all not to loot the things that were not usable by the kill group?  Most of these event items have been for either one specific class, wis casters, or int casters.  It wouldn't have taken that long to decide who got what.  Since there were 3 int casters in the kill group, that's about the only thing (If an int caster item dropped) that would have needed to been rolled on.  Everything else would have been self-explanatory as to who got what.<br>Anyway, just wanting to know people's input on this matter.  Seeing that the shoulders rotted infuriated me...and knowing that the Idol would have most likely done the same makes me feel like I didn't really do anything wrong.  Just wondering here, please do not flame, just give an opinion...<br><br></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
